properties.name: Reference
properties.definition: Reference ID for this specified type in this project (e.g. type 'A-1'), provided, if there is no classification reference to a recognized classification system used.

localizations.name: 参照記号
localizations.definition: このプロジェクトにおける参照記号(例：A-1)。分類コードではなく内部で使用されるプロジェクトタイプとして使用されるもの。

properties.name: Status
properties.definition: Status of the element, predominately used in renovation or retrofitting projects. The status can be assigned to as "New" - element designed as new addition, "Existing" - element exists and remains, "Demolish" - element existed but is to be demolished,  "Temporary" - element will exists only temporary (like a temporary support structure).

localizations.name: 状態
localizations.definition: 要素（主にリノベーションまたは改修プロジェクトにおいて）の状態。 状態は、「新規(New)」－新しく追加される要素。「既存」－要素は存在し、かつ残りもの。「破壊」－要素は存在したが、廃棄されるもの。「一時的」－一時的に存在する要素（一時的にサポートしている構造のようなもの）。

constantValues.name: EXISTING
constantValues.definition: element exists and is to remain

constantValues.name: DEMOLISH
constantValues.definition: element exists but is to be demolished

constantValues.name: TEMPORARY
constantValues.definition: element will exist only temporarily (such as a temporary support structure)

properties.name: Operation
properties.definition: The operational mechanism for the damper operation.

properties.name: Orientation
properties.definition: The intended orientation for the damper as specified by the manufacturer.

properties.name: BladeThickness
properties.definition: The thickness of the damper blade.

properties.name: BladeAction
properties.definition: Blade action.

properties.name: BladeShape
properties.definition: Blade shape. Flat means triple V-groove.

properties.name: BladeEdge
properties.definition: Blade edge.

properties.name: NumberofBlades
properties.definition: Number of blades.

properties.name: FaceArea
properties.definition: Face area open to the airstream.

properties.name: MaximumAirFlowRate
properties.definition: Maximum allowable air flow rate.

properties.name: TemperatureRange
properties.definition: Temperature range.

properties.name: MaximumWorkingPressure
properties.definition: Maximum working pressure.

properties.name: TemperatureRating
properties.definition: Temperature rating.

properties.name: NominalAirFlowRate
properties.definition: Nominal air flow rate.

properties.name: OpenPressureDrop
properties.definition: Total pressure drop across damper.

properties.name: LeakageFullyClosed
properties.definition: Leakage when fully closed.

properties.name: LossCoefficentCurve
properties.definition: Loss coefficient – blade position angle curve; ratio of pressure drop to velocity pressure versus blade angle; C = f (blade angle position).

properties.name: LeakageCurve
properties.definition: Leakage versus pressure drop; Leakage = f (pressure).

properties.name: RegeneratedSoundCurve
properties.definition: Regenerated sound versus air flow rate.

properties.name: FrameType
properties.definition: The type of frame used by the damper (e.g., Standard, Single Flange, Single Reversed Flange, Double Flange, etc.).

properties.name: FrameDepth
properties.definition: The length (or depth) of the damper frame.

properties.name: FrameThickness
properties.definition: The thickness of the damper frame material.

properties.name: CloseOffRating
properties.definition: Close off rating.
